<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>회원 탈퇴 - Dangerous Bros</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="card">
            <h2>회원 탈퇴</h2>
            <p class="warning">정말로 탈퇴하시겠습니까? 탈퇴 시 모든 데이터가 삭제될 수 있습니다.</p>
            <form action="/mypage/delete" method="POST">
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="password">비밀번호 확인</label>
                    <input type="password" id="password" name="password" required placeholder="현재 비밀번호 입력">
                </div>
                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-danger"
                    style="background-color: #ef4444; color: white;">탈퇴하기</button>
            </form>
            <div class="actions">
                <a href="/mypage" class="btn btn-secondary">취소</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>